    <string name="faq1_question">What is the Spending Management App?</string>
    <string name="faq1_answer">This is an app that helps you track and manage personal expenses, set budgets, view statistics and transaction history.</string>
    <string name="faq2_question">How to set up a budget?</string>
    <string name="faq2_answer">You can go to the Budget page and tap the \'+\' button to create a new budget, or chat with AI in natural language to set up a budget easily.</string>
    <string name="faq3_question">How to view expense reports?</string>
    <string name="faq3_answer">Go to Statistics to view expense charts and reports.</string>
    <string name="faq4_question">How to change password?</string>
    <string name="faq4_answer">Go to Account &gt; Change Password to update your new password.</string>
    <string name="faq5_question">How to contact support?</string>
    <string name="faq5_answer">Use the Feedback button or Chat with AI to contact.</string>
    <string name="faq6_question">How to add expenses?</string>
    <string name="faq6_answer">Chat with AI in natural language to add expenses quickly.</string>
    <string name="faq7_question">How to edit or delete expenses?</string>
    <string name="faq7_answer">Chat with AI to edit or delete expenses in natural language.</string>
    <string name="faq8_question">How to edit budget?</string>
    <string name="faq8_answer">You can use AI chat to edit or delete budgets conveniently.</string>
    <string name="faq9_question">How to use Chat with AI?</string>
    <string name="faq9_answer">Tap the \'AI\' button on the menu to open the chat frame. You can use natural language to set up, add, edit, delete expenses and budgets. For example: \'Add 50k expense for food today\' or \'Create 2 million budget for this month\'. AI will help you perform operations easily and quickly.</string>

